text: kmean tosapei avei champoh na pi( mou ham meat) knong rueng del a l laoh ban anounhnhat aoy keat( riebkear cheamuoy braponth robsa kaun chenhchum) laey . noh kuchea chbab robsa a l laoh samreab anak chomnean moun del kanlong phot tow . haey kechchakar robsa a l laoh kuchea kar kamnt del trauv ban kamnt ruoch
